dct_title_s: City and County of the City of Chester. Town and Country Planning Act 1947. Town map
dct_description_sm: Chester Municipal Planning Office. Map is part of a 66p. Report: "Town and Country Planning Act. 1947. Development Plan for the City and County of the City of Chester. Written analysis forming part of the Report of the Survey." The Library does not have a copy of this report. Reproduced from the Ordnance Survey map with the sanction of the H. M. Stationery Office.
